{"tid":1300612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[前列線社工] 我地一早自發跑到hihi   林鄭你仲好意思講係你動員？","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:42:24.000Z","uid":276857,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"03bb35b12ffb5f4dbc3b1cdf001c189530ed2846","tid":1300612,"uid":276857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「一群周街跑到hihi嘅社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">問朋友借AC POST，勿起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n「林鄭政府攪屎棍，攪到個社會立立亂💩」。就係因為條送中條例，一二百萬人上街遊行、差佬爆seed打市民、全港大集合自發抗爭，甚至漫延到呢幾日大量後生仔情緒勁差。<br />\n<br />\n屌你林鄭竟然話「已動員非政府機構，提供輔導服務，期望盡量減低現時社會瀰漫的負面情緒」？！仆街啦你，<span style=\"color: red;\">你攪屎棍攪到周圍都係，要我地班社工幫你執屎？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社工撚表示村民唔係淨係要呢啲「執爛攤子」嘅補救工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線社工喺成場運動初期一早就自發參與運動，爭取公義嘅政制同政治環境，呢啲基本嘢啦！唔好講到係為咗執你D屎我地先去做！<br />\n<br />\n社會福利並唔係為咗社會控制，更唔係為咗安撫由政治問題而衍生出黎嘅問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">政治問題，政治解決</span>，林鄭咪撚一味傳波，我哋成班社工撚都拒絕一切因為政府問題而追加嘅福利撥款，更加拒絕成為仆街政權嘅幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n最後我哋仲想講，我哋一班社工一路由網上救人到網下搵義士，一定同香港人一齊。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">細路有事，社工一定撐到底！香港人加油！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVJar5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVJar5q.jpg&h=b4031a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12cbc2b465c36721cad84753c74b2848803ba5d","tid":1300612,"uid":159913,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔係佢搞壇嘢出嚟，邊有咁多case<br />\n確實係佢動員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf80153aa8927475a934875c5dee787c2a179407","tid":1300612,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03bb35b12ffb5f4dbc3b1cdf001c189530ed2846","tid":1300612,"uid":276857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「一群周街跑到hihi嘅社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">問朋友借AC POST，勿起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n「林鄭政府攪屎棍，攪到個社會立立亂💩」。就係因為條送中條例，一二百萬人上街遊行、差佬爆seed打市民、全港大集合自發抗爭，甚至漫延到呢幾日大量後生仔情緒勁差。<br />\n<br />\n屌你林鄭竟然話「已動員非政府機構，提供輔導服務，期望盡量減低現時社會瀰漫的負面情緒」？！仆街啦你，<span style=\"color: red;\">你攪屎棍攪到周圍都係，要我地班社工幫你執屎？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社工撚表示村民唔係淨係要呢啲「執爛攤子」嘅補救工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線社工喺成場運動初期一早就自發參與運動，爭取公義嘅政制同政治環境，呢啲基本嘢啦！唔好講到係為咗執你D屎我地先去做！<br />\n<br />\n社會福利並唔係為咗社會控制，更唔係為咗安撫由政治問題而衍生出黎嘅問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">政治問題，政治解決</span>，林鄭咪撚一味傳波，我哋成班社工撚都拒絕一切因為政府問題而追加嘅福利撥款，更加拒絕成為仆街政權嘅幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n最後我哋仲想講，我哋一班社工一路由網上救人到網下搵義士，一定同香港人一齊。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span styl